for executing these files simply copy and paste the file contents and then save the file with the same name as the main class and with extension .java,
then go into the cmd or terminal and navigate to the folder where the file is saved and compile it by using the command
"javac [file-name].java" for example the file name is Calculator, type "javac Calculator.java"
then run the java file using the comman 
java [file-name] for example the Calculator file we compiled right now can be run by using the command "java Calculator"
